@startuml
title Create Study Group Activity Diagram

start
:1. Open create study group page;
:2. Enter group name;
:3. Enter subject;
:4. Enter study topics;
:5. Define availability schedule;
:6. Set required skill level;
:7. Enter maximum number of students;
:8. Add group description;
:9. Submit group creation request;
:10. Validate group details;

if (11. Details valid?) then (Yes)
  :12. Create study group;
  :13. Store group information in database;
  :14. Display creation confirmation;
else (No)
  :15. Show validation error;
endif

stop

note right
Activity Description:
1. Student opens the group creation interface.
2. Group name is provided.
3. Subject for study group is entered.
4. Topics covered in the group are specified.
5. Study availability schedule is defined.
6. Required skill level is selected.
7. Maximum number of students allowed is set.
8. Student adds group description.
9. Creation request is submitted.
10. System validates entered details.
11. Validation decision is performed.
12. Study group is created.
13. Group data stored in database.
14. Confirmation message displayed.
15. Error message shown if validation fails.
end note
@enduml